These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: chinese, argentine, pakistani, nigerian
1. Nationality:argentine is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:nigerian is between Nationality:chinese and Nationality:argentine##2
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Nationality:chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | argentine | pakistani |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: radish, pineapple, lime, raspberry
1. Food:radish is on the left of Food:raspberry##1
2. Food:pineapple is in an odd position##4
3. Food:pineapple is on the left or right of Food:radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pineapple | radish | raspberry | lime |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: epic, adventure, romance, sports
1. Movie-Genre:sports is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:epic##3
2. Movie-Genre:epic is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:romance is between Movie-Genre:sports and Movie-Genre:adventure##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | sports | romance | adventure |

 #################################
 
