.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: tomato, banana, papaya, asparagus
1. Food:banana == Food:banana##1
2. Food:asparagus is on the left or right of Food:papaya##3
3. Food:papaya is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:tomato is in an even position##4
5. Food:asparagus is on the left of Food:banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | papaya | asparagus | banana | tomato |

